 AI Resume Analyzer

AI-powered resume analyzer that scores your resume against 
any job description and suggests improvements instantly.

 Features
- PDF resume upload with text extraction
- ATS keyword match scoring
- Missing keyword detection  
- AI-powered bullet point rewriter
- Top 3 actionable improvements

 Tech Stack
- React + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS
- Groq LLaMA AI API
- Supabase
- Deployed on Netlify

